Would everyone please stop just walking up to the CF and knocking on the door 
or walking in?! The shields are up, and the defences on alert. They would 
probably open fire.

::Grimmler::

Coming back from patrol, Grimmler lands behind Shockarat, his gun out just in 
case.

"May I help you," he asks the bot, walking up behind him.
